        {
            "title": "佑駕創新與印度STL訂諒解備忘 推動輔助駕駛系統在印度部署",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">佑駕創新(02431)公布，與印度Sterling Tools Limited (STL)簽署諒解備忘錄，以推進輔助駕駛系統及駕駛員狀態監測系統在印度的部署。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"佑駕創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/Minieye-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"佑駕創新官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/Minieye-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">佑駕創新官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司指出，今次合作標誌公司進軍印度市場的初步舉措，體現更廣泛的海外擴張戰略。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據公告介紹，成立於1979年的STL，是印度領先是高強度冷鐓汽車緊固件製造商，產品應用於乘用車、兩輪摩托車、商用車及工程機械設備，STL股份於印度證交所及孟買證交所上市。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595785-%e4%bd%91%e9%a7%95%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e8%88%87%e5%8d%b0%e5%ba%a6stl%e8%a8%82%e8%ab%92%e8%a7%a3%e5%82%99%e5%bf%98-%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e8%bc%94%e5%8a%a9%e9%a7%95%e9%a7%9b%e7%b3%bb%e7%b5%b1%e5%9c%a8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/Minieye.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 08:49:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "零食商鳴鳴很忙招股入場費近2.39萬元    集資逾33億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地連鎖零食商鳴鳴很忙(01768)今日起招股，每股H股招股價229.6元至236.6元，一手100股23898.62元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全球發售逾1410萬股H股，香港公開發售佔10%，其餘國際配售。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：鳴鳴很忙官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260107_FI_source-web_busyming.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：鳴鳴很忙官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260107_FI_source-web_busyming.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：鳴鳴很忙官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集資最多約33.4億元，約25%用於提升供應鏈能力及產品開發能力，其餘用於門店網絡升級、品牌建設、提升數字化水平等。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">高盛、華泰國際為聯席保薦人。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司持有「零食很忙」及「趙一鳴零食」兩個品牌，主要透過加盟模式經營，是內地最大連鎖休閒食品飲料零售商。去年首9個月商品交易總額(GMV)為661億元人民幣，按年升近75%，毛利率升2.5個百分點至9.7%，淨利潤率升1.6個百分點至3.4%。至去年9月底，在內地有逾1.95萬家店，約59%位於縣城及鄉鎮。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">股份將於下周三主板掛牌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595720-%e9%9b%b6%e9%a3%9f%e5%95%86%e9%b3%b4%e9%b3%b4%e5%be%88%e5%bf%99%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a5%e5%a0%b4%e8%b2%bb%e8%bf%912-39%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e9%80%be33%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01768.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 08:49:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中集安瑞科折讓7.73%配股籌7.8億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中集安瑞科(03899)公布，擬配股集貟7.8億元；配股價9.79元，較該股昨收市價10.61元折讓約7.73%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中集安瑞科官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/03899-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中集安瑞科官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/03899-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中集安瑞科官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價10.742元計，配股價較之折讓8.86%，較前10個交易日平均收市價10.418元則折讓6.03%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集資淨額約7.74億元，約50%用於清潔能源業務的資本性支出；其餘約50%用於一般業務運作。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595771-%e4%b8%ad%e9%9b%86%e5%ae%89%e7%91%9e%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%937-73%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c7-8%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/03899-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 08:44:02",
